{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a20eebc951","title":"毛泽东对集宁军分区三反斗争情况报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e160252d3b","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":14,"articleId":"a20eebc951"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"05756d0405","type":"title","text":"毛泽东对集宁军分区三反斗争情况报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a20eebc951"},{"id":"477452405c","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a20eebc951"},{"id":"8ad52f68d8","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区，志愿军，并转各级军区和各军：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a20eebc951"},{"id":"cbac04ff72","type":"paragraph","text":"我们愿意看见各级军区和各军有像集宁分区这样的检讨，不愿意看那些好像太平无事的报告。集宁分区只说了浪费和生活腐化，还没有提到贪污事件。像一个军分区一定有大批的贪污犯，望各地严格注意。一切没有切实暴露问题和解决问题的机关和部队，必须从头做过，做好了三反再做整编，三反一天没有做好即一天不进行整编。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a20eebc951"},{"id":"9b86268954","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a20eebc951"}],"page":{"id":"85de3e1265","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a20eebc951","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}